{"TopicId":175182,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Help!","CreatedByName":"ReigningKing","CreatedById":189111,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-22T01:29:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ReigningKing","CreatedById":189111,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-22T01:29:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:13px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:13px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:#555555;font-size:13px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\nI am fairly new to the game and need some guidance on... well many things actually but, its obvious the without a good spacecraft i\u0027m not going to get far.\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\nWith this being said can anyone guide me in the direction of a video or tutorial that can help me understand simple rocket engineering and the physics around it?\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Noobton","CreatedById":114094,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-22T02:22:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey RK, welcome to the forums. Scott Manley taught me almost everything I know about KSP, and even though his videos are a old now, all the principles are still valid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLYu7z3I8tdEmqpOkQZCl5SZB5t0vXuxE0\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ReigningKing","CreatedById":189111,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-23T02:16:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223383594\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022175182\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221526955760\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022114094\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Noobton\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n23 hours ago, Noobton said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey RK, welcome to the forums. Scott Manley taught me almost everything I know about KSP, and even though his videos are a old now, all the principles are still valid.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLYu7z3I8tdEmqpOkQZCl5SZB5t0vXuxE0\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthank you very much! this helped extremely, i am not \u0022a noob\u0022 at the game but i am not a rocket scientist either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-23T02:20:20Z\u0022 title=\u002205/23/2018 02:20  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 23, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by ReigningKing\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Eim dumby head\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-23T10:43:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts kinda simple. You throw stuff onr way, stuff throws you the other way. Engines throw fuel away very quickly, so rockets fly. I believe you can open the tutorial on this forum and search for guides for beginners.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lego_Prodigy","CreatedById":187421,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-23T12:58:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTbh, I\u00A0learned most of what i know about KSP from messing with it and also from the in game tutorials. those can be helpful. also, apply real world principles such as the thrust-lift-drag-weight of planes and aerodynamics (meaning make it as streamlined as possible so that it goes thru atmosphere nicely).\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-05-23T12:59:00Z\u0022 title=\u002205/23/2018 12:59  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EMay 23, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Lego_Prodigy\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}